Hi Dave, 
On first listen I&#39;m hearing &quot;Oh that (or &quot;Oh now&quot;).... this is is 
dead people&quot;. Listened to this in WMP. Then I loaded it into Cool 
Edit and slowed it down a bit but still hearing the same thing. 
Either way, could not discern what was being said immediately before 
&#39;this is dead people&quot; but this part came in very clearly where even 
if you had not mentioned ahead of time what was being said in that 
section, I too would be saying that this is what&#39;s being said there. 
What&#39;s interesting is &#39;they&#39; often identify themselves as &#39;dead 
people&#39; and I know this because many others have recorded EVP where 
they are saying that too though I myself have never gotten an EVP 
saying that.  
At any rate, I&#39;ve personally never recorded an EVP or listened to any 
other EVP recorded by others where they are saying that are spirits 
or ghosts, or angels or discarnates in regards to general terms to 
WHAT they are. 




